import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='Penicillin', kde=True)
    plt.title('What is the distribution of Penicillin effectiveness against the bacteria?', wrap=True)
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    ax = sns.histplot(data=data, x='Streptomycin', kde=True)
    ax.set_xlabel('Streptomycin effectiveness')
    ax.set_ylabel('Count')
    ax.xaxis.label.set_rotation(0)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.title('What is the distribution of Streptomycin effectiveness against the bacteria?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
